name: Asemic Palimpsest #008
description:
This is #008 of "Asemic Palimpsest "

The following generative series is a set of 8 unique pieces that use an asemic writing system. A Palimsest is a manuscript in which the previous text was altered and the manuscript reused. One can also think of a wall in which graffiti was painted over and drawn on again. 

The piece is 1000x1000 in order to ensure the ability to display on larger displays.

On Twitter: @generatecoll / Instagram: @generate.collective (2021)
